snippet.title: D.U.C.K. | Release trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1820770/DUCK_Dangerous_Ultimate_Cartridge_Kidnapper/
"D.U.C.K.: Dangerous Ultimate Cartridge Kidnapper" is already available on Steam! 100 different microgames, a few single and "hotseat" modes, 16 set panels, extras, secret quests, passcards, ducks... lots of ducks!!! Cozy art and various pixel-art style for the microgames! Variety and surprises everywhere. Test your gamer skills and help the ducklings in their fight against the D.U.C.K - wily spirit!
